snippet.title: PAC MAN MUSEUM + - Arcade Trailer
snippet.description:
PAC-MAN MUSEUM + will be here on May 27, 2022! Build your own virtual PAC-MAN arcade with wallpapers, figures, and arcade machines that you unlock by completing missions!

It's an experience that no PAC-MAN fan should miss!

PAC-MAN MUSEUM + is coming soon to PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, and PC, with Day One Xbox Game Pass support!

Follow us on:
Web: https://www.bandainamcoent.eu
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/bandainamcoeu
